title: Occurrence data in Arctos bulkloader format
Data for fungal specimens to be sequenced
caption: Data exported from the [2020 Kenai Peninsula fungal sequencing](https://www.inaturalist.org/projects/2020-kenai-peninsula-fungal-sequencing) iNaturalist project following the [guidelines of the Fungal Diversity Survey](https://fundis.org/sequence/sequence/submit-tissue).
